summary: This mod adds 22 more dark elves to the game, per a user request. The majority are marriage candidates and are spread across the province. No DLC required.
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds 22 more dark elves to the base Skyrim continent. Each of these dark elves are unique and are spread throughout the province. Below are a list of each of them and where you might find them (since a few of them wander on the roads):

Dark Brotherhood:

Saviven Baraer - She is a member of the Dark Brotherhood. (Can Marry)

Ondaeth Ulvlayn - He is a member of the Dark Brotherhood. (Can Marry)

Riften:

Androth Velnndel - He is a mercenary for hire at the inn. (Can Marry)

Biloi Veleram - He is a member of the Thieves Guild. (Can Marry)

Gurveso Saleothran - She is a member of the Thieves Guild. (Can Marry)

Rorikstead:

Barendresa Garvromo - She is a mercenary for hire at the inn. (Can Marry)

Ernifar Adasds - He is a guard in the Town of Rorikstead.

Ondapar Tunemalvel - He is a bard at the Rorikstead inn. (Can Marry)

Solitude:

Aryili Arobhan - She is a member of the Bards College (can marry)

Balaben Ertira - He is a member of the Bards College (can marry)

Whiterun:

Idrinah Dulhren - She is a guard for the City of Whiterun.

Golaayn Arenys - He is a College of Winterhold Mage staying at Whiterun. (Can Marry)

Orvha Terillian - She is a member of the Companions. (Can Marry)

Sodrer Hlarvayn - He is a member of the Companions. (Can Marry)

Windhelm:

Faruira Dratngi - She is a College of Winterhold Mage staying at Windhelm. (Can Marry)

Nathanda Moloil - She is a bard at the New Gnisis Corner Club in Windhelm. (Can Marry)

Winterhold:

Arelaso Nulas - He is a mage at the College of Winterhold. (Can Marry)

Duldvos Daren - He is a mage at the College of Winterhold. (Can Marry)

Mordenu Rineri - She is a mage at the College of Winterhold. (Can Marry)

Tadarose Llendus - She is a mage at the College of Winterhold. (Can Marry)

Wilderness:

Tiliile Urnsngi - She is a wandering adventurer on the west side of Skyrim. Places of stop include Whiterun, Morthal, Markarth, Solitude, and Dawnstar.

Uthrdstar Meryendus - He is a wandering adventurer on the east side of Skyrim. Places of stop include Whiterun, Windhelm, Winterhold, and Riften.

Changelog:
v1.3:
-Added 2 NPCs to the Bards College
v1.2:
-Changed voice type for the male bard to fix the bard.
V1.1:
-Added Light Foot to the mercenaries.
-Changed the armor from Leather to Thieves Guild Armor for the Thieves Guild members.
V1:
-The initial release.

Known Bugs:
None at this time.
